## 4. Authentication & RBAC Schema

Design:

users

roles

permissions

role_permissions

user_roles

Requirements:

- many-to-many user-role
- many-to-many role-permission
- support future multi-role users
- soft delete capable

Include:

- created_at
- updated_at
- created_by
- updated_by

where appropriate.

