Support:

- resume uploads
- AI screening
- scoring
- ranking
- recruiter comments
- status tracking

Store:

- extracted skills
- matched skills
- missing skills
- AI score
- recommendation
- explanation

Use JSONB where beneficial.

---

## 7. Attendance Module Schema

Design:

attendance_records

attendance_corrections

attendance_statuses

Requirements:

Support:

- check in
- check out
- work duration
- attendance status
- manual corrections
- reporting

