## 8. Leave Management Schema

Design:

leave_types

leave_balances

leave_requests

leave_approvals

Requirements:

Support:

- approval workflow
- balances
- future multi-level approvals

---

## 9. Performance Management Schema

Design:

performance_cycles

performance_reviews

performance_metrics

employee_metric_scores

performance_feedback

Requirements:

Support:

- KPI tracking
- ratings
- manager reviews
- historical evaluations

